sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client<br/>(Dashboard/CLI)
    participant IstioGW as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant BFF as UI BFF<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Proxy as model-registry (proxy)<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Catalog as model-catalog-server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant CatalogDB as PostgreSQL (catalog)<br/>5432/TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as model-registry-controller<br/>8081/TCP
    participant CSI as CSI Storage Initializer
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/OCI)
    participant HF as Hugging Face API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client, DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API
        Client->>IstioGW: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Platform auth
        IstioGW->>Proxy: Forward (Istio mTLS)<br/>ISTIO_MUTUAL
        Proxy->>DB: INSERT registered_model<br/>Auth: Username/password
        DB-->>Proxy: Success
        Proxy-->>IstioGW: 201 Created (JSON)
        IstioGW-->>Client: Model registered
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Controller, DB: Flow 2: InferenceService Reconciliation
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event: InferenceService created<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>Proxy: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/inference_services<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Proxy->>DB: INSERT inference_service
        DB-->>Proxy: Success
        Proxy-->>Controller: 201 Created
        Controller->>K8sAPI: PATCH InferenceService labels/finalizers<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over CSI, Storage: Flow 3: Model Download via CSI Storage Initializer
        CSI->>Proxy: GET model artifact URI<br/>model-registry://model/version
        Proxy->>DB: SELECT artifact_uri
        DB-->>Proxy: s3://bucket/model.tar.gz
        Proxy-->>CSI: Resolved storage URI
        CSI->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>Auth: Storage credentials (TLS 1.2+)
        Storage-->>CSI: Model files
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 245)
        Note over Client, CatalogDB: Flow 5: UI Model Browsing
        Client->>BFF: GET /api/v1/model_registry/myregistry/registered_models<br/>Auth: User token
        BFF->>Proxy: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: Forwarded token
        Proxy->>DB: SELECT registered_models
        DB-->>Proxy: Model list
        Proxy-->>BFF: JSON response
        BFF->>Catalog: GET /api/model_catalog/v1alpha1/catalog_models<br/>Auth: Forwarded token
        Catalog->>CatalogDB: SELECT catalog_models
        CatalogDB-->>Catalog: Catalog data
        Catalog->>HF: GET model metadata<br/>Auth: API key (optional)
        HF-->>Catalog: Model metadata
        Catalog-->>BFF: Catalog models
        BFF-->>Client: Combined UI response
    end
